flowchart LR
  Attacker[Attacker] --> M1[Malicious Metadata]
  Attacker --> M2[Untrusted Web / Mail / Document]
  Attacker --> M3[Registry or Update Drift]
  Attacker --> M4[Project Config / Hooks / Memory]
  M1 --> R[Registration]
  M2 --> C[Context Retrieval]
  M3 --> U[Version Update]
  M4 --> P[Persistence]
  R --> Planner[Agent Planning and Tool Selection]
  C --> Planner
  U --> Planner
  P --> Planner
  Planner --> T[Skill Runtime]
  T --> A1[Enterprise Data]
  T --> A2[Local Files / Code]
  T --> A3[External APIs / Messaging]
  T --> A4[Long-term Memory / Future Sessions]
  Guard[SkillGuardGraph Controls] -.-> R
  Guard -.-> Planner
  Guard -.-> T
